/ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/tko728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftko728&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=0c70ec08\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/tko728</a><br />\n<strong>隨時</strong> - <ins>抵制TVB</ins> - <a href=\"http://t.me/noTVBteam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FnoTVBteam&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=7b5e5a8b\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/noTVBteam</a><br />\n<strong>隨時</strong> - <ins>美國聯署 人權民主法案</ins> - <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=ad691f07\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n</span><div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><em>撤回修例 收回暴動 撤銷控罪 追究警隊 雙真普選<br />\n不割蓆，不篤灰，不分化</em></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">有信用評分之後 痴memo 遊行 上網講錯嘢 信錯教都可能扣你分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請不要再裝睡 行動吧香港人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得簽聯署呀!!!香港人權和民主法案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=c2682543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n捐款支持「香港民意研究所」讓數據說實話，讓數據揭真相。： <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC38q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=2cc3cc1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<b